<p><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 34px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">元旦，即公历的1月1日，是世界上多数国家通称的“新年”。元，所谓“始”，凡数之始称为“元”；旦，谓“日”。“元旦”即“初始之日”的意思，就是要人们以蓬勃朝气来迎接崭新的一年。</span></p><p></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">感谢各位老师在这一年的陪伴和关照</span><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px;">我们在这里祝福所有老师</span><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px;">2023年平安喜乐、万事胜意</span><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px;">同时也祝福您及您的家人心有所成</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240305/1709645865361054663.jpg" title="1709645865361054663.jpg" alt="c3ccca28826016a7e690e3c1389fd153.jpg" width="376" height="286" style="width: 376px; height: 286px;"/></p>